{
  "stem": "26672.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They wanted me very much to come live with him and for me to go to college, get an education, which I never had.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, um, I felt it was wrong of me to stay on, because things were very, very tough for them even.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was in the army.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was trying to bring up two daughters himself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, uh, things were not easy, and I felt that I should give them a little bit rest.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Minucha.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sa-- one-- the oldest one is Sarah and the second one is Shoshana.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we still very close.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Although they marry and aunt and uncle died.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- But I'm close to my cousins.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we're very much in touch with each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, exactly what happened-- I mean, I'm sure after awhile they stopped coming over to find, and they occupied Poland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We came back into town, and things carried on as normal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, um, sudden they created a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ghetto must have been-- must have been-- ghetto must have been I would reckon '40, '41 they establish a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, uh, and they designate a certain area.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were lucky that our house was in the ghetto, so we didn't have to move out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But a lot of people came in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there's one, uh, one man in Israel, at the moment, called Moishe Oppenheim that lived-- he spent, his family, spent time in our house.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I'm sure their others, but I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, until-- till the war, it was only just our own family, but then, obviously, my mother's sisters and brother came in and this family, Oppenheim, came in.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there must have been others, as well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was quite a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not very good.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not very good.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
